                    <span>Ms. Harris shows uncommon sensitivity in her choice of authors. I was moved to tears of joy and sorrow on several occasions.  Without a doubt Ms Harris's work will rank as one of the most thoughful and provocative  volumes of how we, as human beings, deal with grief and ultimately move on.</span>
                  
              
